{% block pagecontent %}
	<h1>Manga and Anime Society Kharagpur</h1>
	<div class="text" style="text-align: left;">
		<p>
			Greetings from <b>MANGA AND ANIME SOCIETY KHARAGPUR (MASK)</b>. We are a society of enthusiastic otakus with a keen interest in anime, mangas, manhwas and more, working to make some more
		</p><br/>
		<h2> History </h2>
		<p>
			Being among the newer societies of IIT Kharagpur, MASK was established in 2020 when anime was gaining popularity at an incredible rate due to the lockdown. 
			Our founding members wanted to create a place to spread anime culture at IIT Kharagpur and make a place for anime fans to come together and share their enthusiasm.
		</p>
		<br/>
		<h2> What We Do Over Here </h2>
		<p>
			At MASK, we involve ourselves in a variety of things. We regularly release anime-related content such as <a href="/newsletters">newsletters</a>, <a href="/videos">AMVs</a>, <a href="/art">fan arts</a> etc. We also hold <a href="/events">events</a> for fellow anime enthusiasts on and around the campus. Except them, we also have some activites exclusive for the members of the society.
		</p>
		<br/>
		<p>
			We also accept fan art and AMVs from outside society and publish them on social media while featuring the creator. If you want to make any AMV/ fanart submissions, you can do it <a href="/submissions">here</a>.
		</p>
		<br/>
		<h2> Teams </h2>
		<p>
			We have five teams which are responsible for various aspects of our society.
		</p>
		<br/>
		<p>
			<div id="teams-container">
				<div class="team-border">
					<h4>AMV Team</h4>
					<p>AMV team showcases their creativity on platforms like youtube and instagram in form AMVs, Reels and Memes for all to enjoy.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="team-border">
					<h4>Design and Arts Team</h4>
					<p>The Design and Arts team is involved in making fan arts. They also design our merch, newsletter coverpages and more.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="team-border">
					<h4>Media and Newsletter Team</h4>
					<p>Just like the name suggests, the Media and Newsletter team is in charge of handling our social media and responsible for releasing newsletters.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="team-border">
					<h4>Quiz Team</h4>
					<p>The Quiz team works on making engaging anime quizzes and puzzles for various events, competition and newsletter.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="team-border">
					<h4>Web Development</h4>
					<p>WebDev team ensures the smooth digital experiences, managing our website and making it easy for everyone to connect.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</p>
		<br/>
	</div>
